sentences: Nathaniel David Rateliff (born October 7, 1978) is an American singer and songwriter based in Denver, Colorado, whose influences are described as folk, Americana and vintage rhythm & blues.
Rateliff has performed with a backing band called the Night Sweats for an R&B side project he formed in 2013.
Rateliff was born in St. Louis, Missouri, on October 7, 1978.
